{"tid":10083,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖 澳洲土人切開尿道的分割禮 陰莖一分為二","createTime":"2016-11-28T20:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T20:31:58.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1940b0a57930235ce8cbebf47c3b16c52d8d6a2","tid":10083,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:26:35.000Z","msg":"「分割禮」是澳洲原住民最為神秘的儀式，男性陰莖會從根部縱向剖到尿道口，讓生殖器像條切開的香腸一樣展開。而且裂縫會一點一點擴大，變成一個完全開放的通道，使尿道暴露在外，因此經過此儀式的男性往往要坐著尿尿。<br />\n<br />\n對澳洲男性來說，「分割禮」是一種成年的象徵，性快感則是它的附加好處，然而因此感染的風險也相當高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖 <br />\n<a href=\"http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Penile_subincision\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FPenile_subincision&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJ2N6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=2b244131\" target=\"_blank\">http://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Penile_subincision</a>"},{"pid":"33ed6fff319d64e03b29cbc0ef11220248ad4770","tid":10083,"uid":23407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:27:46.000Z","msg":"講還講"},{"pid":"cccfeaaf0af81119c359f50b3d813177c5435870","tid":10083,"uid":26998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:30:08.000Z","msg":"女人睇到都好撚不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76af6e0c961a2b9cdfd571fa5e90334ec0f8d3f8","tid":10083,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好痛"},{"pid":"08d59796a10a57ff994b67c102d8c2e0e614ebba","tid":10083,"uid":8304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:40:31.000Z","msg":"兩碌鳩巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb524564b22abcd7a2daa90f44a0ba3b3e03ded2","tid":10083,"uid":114